# Salesforce App Builder Practice Web App

Test yourself with realistic mock exams for the Salesforce Admin Certification.  
No installation, no account needed — just visit and start practising from any device!  
Includes instant correction, progress tracking, and smart review of failed questions.

---

## How to Use

- Open in any browser or mobile: [GH Pages link will appear here]
- Choose between study by unit or full exam mode.
- Get instant feedback and explanations for every question.
- End the exam early at any time and review your results.
- Updates are automatic — every time you revisit the page, you get the latest version.

## Features

- 150+ curated Salesforce App Builder certification questions
- Study by topic/unit or take randomized full exams
- Multi-device compatible (phone/tablet/desktop)
- No logins, no downloads
- Free and always updated

## Author

Built by a Salesforce developer for the community.

